Synopsis: Retrieves the supported encryption types based on the specified value.
Description: This function returns the list of encryption types supported by Active Directory based on the provided value. Each encryption type is represented by a string.
Notes: This function is designed to provide information about encryption types supported by Active Directory.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Get-ADEncryptionTypes -Value 24
Retrieves the following encryption types:
- AES128-CTS-HMAC-SHA1-96
- AES256-CTS-HMAC-SHA1-96
